  "unresolved_reason": "The L2 case replay exposes real rule, pattern, capture and generated-condition facts. L1 internals and the L4 prompt/model/conversion/validation/formatting snapshots are not exposed by current Tools; the manifest records the missing L4 replay rather than pretending those stages are observable. The parse endpoint also stops before downstream customer search, so result-set correctness remains outside this trace scope.",
